{"tid":1826184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公帑養黃牛】揭科技園涉近百萬「培育」黃牛飛網站 創辦人自比Uber：係社會嘅創新","createTime":"2020-01-16T02:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T04:15:49.000Z","uid":78546,"like":24,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5d074f75de0d294b48071e46361d6f8011475290","tid":1826184,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200116&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60486947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200116%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60486947&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=e05c43dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200116%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60486947&h=5edea966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200116&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60486947</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港演唱會「黃牛飛」問題多年來一直困擾樂迷，雖然政府有意加強罰則，計劃將炒賣紅館門票行為刑事化。但問題至今仍未有改善跡象。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》發現，香港「黃牛飛」<a href=\"http://龍頭Ticketbuynow.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%BE%8D%E9%A0%ADTicketbuynow.com&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=945b7359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">龍頭Ticketbuynow.com</a>，由Inspirr Group Limited（現改名為Innoticket）營運，竟是科技園公司 2017年度「創業培育計劃」成功畢業的68間培育公司之一。而同屆畢業亦包括著名Kickstarter騙局，「咖啡兄弟」幕後公司Nbition。<br />\n有知情人士指，本是設freelance招聘網站的Inspirr，因經營不理想，持續下去恐未能畢業。科技園欲「谷高」培育計劃成功率，在園方的同意下，決定將業務轉至「炒黃牛飛」，令公司收入大增，最終成功達到科技園要求順利畢業，現更成為全港最大「黃牛」集團。根據計劃，每間培育公司成員可獲最高86萬元資助。<br />\n政府一方面向觀眾展示打擊「黃牛」決心，另方面卻利用公帑「培育」黃牛飛網站。Innoticket創辦人伍偉華（Andy Ng）直認公司由科技園資助，更自比Uber，指「係社會嘅創新」。"},{"pid":"e3c1d5c74ce56ebca40d2bc2470f80bc8b105d77","tid":1826184,"uid":48026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"票源邊到黎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a765ace47b3479cc03f626656a16d7acae69e71e","tid":1826184,"uid":78546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:30:27.000Z","msg":"早前有傳媒混入全港最大「黃牛」集團之一，直擊網上搶票過程，並引述其負責人伍錦泉一直嚴密監視「搶票員」工作情況。報道稱程式雖然成功搶購數百張演唱會門票，但只屬低端科技<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查Ticketbuynow網站，現時主打將於2月舉行的劉德華香港演唱會。尾場前5行「握手位」，原價980元的門票，售價高達12,500元，比原價貴11.7倍。而原價380元的「山頂位」，售價仍要2,750元，價錢比原價最貴的門票還要高"},{"pid":"5673fd9837b8ce6078bcb9773b5f533e6be1873b","tid":1826184,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"HK no IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c84a17872884d225c705face88d575660d242f","tid":1826184,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3c1d5c74ce56ebca40d2bc2470f80bc8b105d77","tid":1826184,"uid":48026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"票源邊到黎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"南亞 黑社會"},{"pid":"a2863dbedbb67503d54dfbed06c89a921bdb1f15","tid":1826184,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a765ace47b3479cc03f626656a16d7acae69e71e","tid":1826184,"uid":78546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:30:27.000Z","msg":"早前有傳媒混入全港最大「黃牛」集團之一，直擊網上搶票過程，並引述其負責人伍錦泉一直嚴密監視「搶票員」工作情況。報道稱程式雖然成功搶購數百張演唱會門票，但只屬低端科技<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查Ticketbuynow網站，現時主打將於2月舉行的劉德華香港演唱會。尾場前5行「握手位」，原價980元的門票，售價高達12,500元，比原價貴11.7倍。而原價380元的「山頂位」，售價仍要2,750元，價錢比原價最貴的門票還要高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"睇垃圾填海華皮幾嘢"},{"pid":"b9fa57e3edf5962d86bc382cf062157593833dd3","tid":1826184,"uid":84267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"但只屬低端科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130b688de4073000fc3d02eeab70828083b845ba","tid":1826184,"uid":83582,"like":8,"dislike":